From 77e8b6c62c48b6346bbdb2df3e0d925852c6bf3e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Daniel Veillard <veillard@redhat.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Feb 2006 22:50:52 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] * configure.in src/Makefile.am: adding dependency to libxml2
 * include/libvirt.h* src/libvirt.c src/xend_internal.[ch]   src/xml.[ch]:
 added XML parsing for Xen domain descriptions   needed for creates, plugged
 in a converter to s-exp and   xend call. Modified the virDomainCreateLinux()
 to reflect   that XML based description. Seems to work. *
 python/tests/create.py: added a test case which seems to work   not tested
 much yet * docs/*: regenerated Daniel

---
